title: Report opened files whose names match a given regex
name: regex.stp
keywords: regex
subsystem: any
status: experimental
exit: user-controlled
scope: system-wide
description: Uses the regex functionality to detect opened files whose names match a given pattern (in this case, ending with an extension showing them to be an archive).
test_check: stap -p4 regex.stp
test_installcheck: stap regex.stp -c "sleep 0.2"
